Cancelled my Home Depot credit card and told them exactly why. However, while on the site to close my shopping account, I found something pretty scary. They use automated license plate recognition in their parking lots and save that data. To anyone at risk, please be aware. #boycotthomedepot

Toyota? Never. That includes Suburu and Mazda hybrids which use Toyota technology. Too bad, we were looking to replace an old car next year with a hybrid. This does help narrow down our options though. #boycottToyota

Philadelphia and the world have lost a legend with the passing of Pierre Robert. He played more Dead than any other DJ over the past four decades, and Thanksgiving will never be the same in my home without tuning into WMMR and Pierre Robert playing Alice's Restaurant while I cook. RIP legend.
